23rd July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 18 Highlights

Stage 18 is 185km between Gap and Saint Jean de Maurienne. The Col du Glandon at 21.3km at 6.9 per cent is the longest climb on the route, but Les Lacets de Montvernier is a 3.4km climb at 8.2 per cent with 17 hairpins that have to be seen to be believed. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
